{"tid":533650,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"放工途中嬲到傻咗","createTime":"2018-01-19T04:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T05:13:58.000Z","uid":109631,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b93b291d844a38daf70ec4c1c03f7d0206971eba","tid":533650,"uid":109631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:06:06.000Z","msg":"話說撞完車行路仲要拐杖行拐拐下，<br />\n點知琴日放工行去地鐵站，<br />\n就撞到個收佣環保人士叫我幫手，<br />\n話趕時間走就算，唔同你哋嘈，<br />\n點知條仔話：<br />\n「行咁快係咪真係整親架，氣候變化就千真萬確啦」<br />\n<br />\n我火到傻咗，差啲一枝拐杖車埋去<br />\n<br />\n點知我一拎起拐杖隻腳就冇力啦唯有走啦<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想話自己整親有幾慘，係想講<br />\n<br />\n你班人係街同人講嘢前可唔可以諗清楚先<br />\n唔好咁搞笑，會好危險㗎"},{"pid":"741bf991eebb5c957d1584c0e722c4b78b350d06","tid":533650,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:12:59.000Z","msg":"Wa diu 咁撚賤 係我就report佢"},{"pid":"1ecba071b98a3cf17f9417897fb49c8780c59204","tid":533650,"uid":15243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"屌 笑左出聲"},{"pid":"8369686f1272dc9649a9373c2b3d8de3c1e86cf4","tid":533650,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:13:56.000Z","msg":"依家啲人真係唔怕俾人打"},{"pid":"3ff65603eac70a5c73c72869d1eb929981b93048","tid":533650,"uid":109631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ecba071b98a3cf17f9417897fb49c8780c59204","tid":533650,"uid":15243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"屌 笑左出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"其實佢好有急才，諗諗下都幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}